      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Seismic Scares",
        "Client": "A Royal Commandant with Decorum",
        "Description": "When we received a report that\r\na Tigrex had been spotted, we\r\nset out to fell the beast with all\r\nhaste, but when we arrived we\r\nwere ambushed by two of them.\r\nClever beasts! I shall have to rely\r\non you for this one, Hunter.",
